    "Most of the research focuses on the LLMs, an Internet-based platform designed to enable students to engage in peer-to-peer discussions beyond the boundaries of traditional education.",
    "Universities, therefore, have a unique opportunity to reflect on the ethical foundations of AI research and teach students behaviors that support these values.",
    "This is important to ensure that AI models such as LLM promote ethical standards, protect student rights, and enhance educational opportunities.",
    "Figure 16 shows the constraints in higher education.",
